text: Milizac-Guipronvel () is a commune. It is found in the region Brittany in the Finistère department in the northwest of France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2017 and consists of the former communes of Guipronvel (the seat) and Milizac.Arrêté préfectoral 29 June 2016 == References == Category:2017 establishments in France Category:Communes in Finistère
